text: Aarseth is a Norwegian surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Asbjørn Aarseth (1935–2009), Norwegian literary historian * Espen Aarseth (born 1965), Norwegian media scholar * Ivar Aarseth (1889–1972), Norwegian politician * Sverre Aarseth (born 1934), British astronomer * Øystein Aarseth (1968 - 1993), Norwegian musician ==See also== * 9836 Aarseth, main-belt asteroid Category:Norwegian-language surnames
